title: Champion Power Equipment 100743 3-Inch Gas-Powered Semi-Trash Water Transfer Pump with Hose and Wheel Kit
features: COMPLETE SETUP: Everything you need to start pumping - 12-foot suction hose with filter, 25-foot discharge hose, quick cam lock coupler, clamps, adapters, fittings, nylon tape, and storage bag
EFFICIENT: Up to 264 gallons per minute maximum delivery powered by a 224cc Champion OHV engine with a 3-gallon fuel tank and 0.5-quart oil capacity. Includes a wide priming cap for quick startup
SEMI-TRASH: Capable of passing solid waste up to 0.75 inch in diameter, this pump has a 3-inch NPT inlet and outlet, total head of 92 feet and suction head of 26 feet
CONVENIENT: Featuring a durable steel frame, handle and wheel kit with never-flat tires, this pump is easy to move from one job to the next and a cinch to store
CHAMPION SUPPORT: Includes 2-year limited warranty with FREE lifetime technical support from dedicated experts
description: The Champion Power Equipment 100743 3-inch Semi-Trash Gas-Powered Water Transfer Pump with Hose and Wheel Kit comes with everything you need to start pumping (just add oil and gas). Capable of passing solid waste up to 0.75 of an inch in diameter, this transfer pump is the perfect solution for moving water quickly and efficiently. Whether you are draining or refilling your swimming pool, removing water from your basement or draining shallow flooded areas, this unit features a self-priming design that holds prime even when it’s not running (requires initial priming to operate). This lightweight and portable transfer pump has a maximum delivery volume of up to 264 gallons per minute and is capable of passing solid waste up to 0.75 inch in diameter. With a 3-inch NPT inlet outlet, this unit has a total head of 92 feet and a suction head of 26 feet. The complete hose kit provides everything you need to get your pump into action, including a 12-foot suction hose with filter, 25-foot discharge hose, quick cam lock coupler, clamps, adapters, fittings, nylon tape, along with a handy accessory bag to keep everything organized. Champion’s reliable 224cc OHV engine has a 3-gallon fuel tank and 0.5-quart oil capacity (recommended 10W-30) and provides plenty of power for you to move water with confidence and efficiency. Transport your pump from one job to the next with ease thanks to the foldaway handle and never flat tires in the included wheel kit. The shaft seals are made of sturdy silicone carbide. The lightweight and durable steel frame along with this unit’s compact design make it convenient to store your pump until the next time you need it. This water transfer pump is EPA certified and CARB exempt. Buy with confidence - Champion Support and our nationwide network of service centers will back your purchase up with a 2-year limited warranty and FREE lifetime technical support.
